INSTALL
=======

Ubuntu / Linux
--------------

Install the following dependencies

- tools:
$ sudo apt-get install cmake build-essential

- libs:
$ sudo apt-get install libboost-all-dev


OSX
---
$ brew install cmake boost

Then exec: make and it would go, executables would go in build/src/bin

You can execute tests:
$ make test

Windows
-------

BUILD
=====
$ make
$ make test

Binaries al installed in bin directory
